Employee Leave Management System (ELMS)

A complete Spring Boot application to manage employee leave requests, approvals, and leave policies in an organization. 
Built with JWT-based security, role-based access control, scheduled leave accrual, and integrated with Swagger documentation.

Features
JWT Authentication & Role-based Authorization
        Roles: ADMIN, MANAGER, EMPLOYEE

Apply, Approve & Reject Leave Requests
